rest_of_day_open: I think that the rest of my week will be good, as I have been spending a lot of time outside hiking and enjoying nature, and will continue to do so. I also have been spending a lot of time working on personal things and online work through surveys and studies.
critical_positive: We were both from the same area (Chicagoland area), and this allowed us to connect. We also were both students of the University of Illinois system, me being from Urbana-champaign, and him studying at the University of Illinois - Chicago program. We also were both STEM majors who likely don't want to follow the path of our major.
critical_negative: It is slightly hard to talk through video chat, as it is easier to cut each other off and get confused. It is also slightly harder to pick up on body language in a video chat, so it is easier to be confused about the message someone is sending your way.
